#15 reset password of all users

Summary: In forgot password, it asks to enter email, and we do so, it says it resets the password and it will send the new password in email.
Steps to reproduce: Create a list of users using this website and Click on login, then Forgot password, then enter a email and click reset and capture the request in burp. In burp, send the request to intruder, and add the value of Email. Now paste the list of users of the application and start attack.
Impact: Due to this bug, an attacker can reset password of all legit users without their knowledge, and here most of the users created account using fake email. So it will cause permanent account lockout.
